<i>noun</i>: 호객 [호객], 탄원 [타ː눤] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호객 [호객]</dt><br>
<dd>solicitation; touting</dd><br>
<dd>물건 등을 팔기 위해 손님을 부름.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of hailing a potential customer to sell goods, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>탄원 [타ː눤]</dt><br>
<dd>entreaty; solicitation; petition</dd><br>
<dd>억울하거나 딱한 사정을 남에게 알려 도와주기를 간절히 바람.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of informing someone of one's unfair or pitiful situation, earnestly seeking help.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>